items.description: Ancient Artifact found in the Tower.  Once found, the effect is activated at the bottom of your Skill Perks section.

items.name: Spooky Pie
items.description_ext:
How to frighten your crops with a Spooky Pie:
  1. Plant 4 individual seeds (4 of a single type, 4 different types, or mix it up)
  2. Activate your pie by going to the item details for the Spooky Pie and hit 'Use this item'
  3. Harvest each of your 4 crops when they are finished growing, or after using a grape juice
  4. Receive each of the 4 harvested crops and any other items the individual crop can produce (gold crops, runestones, etc)

EXAMPLE: If you plant a carrot, when you harvest the carrot you would receive an extra carrot, a gold carrot and Runestone 01, guaranteed! This pie works with any crop, but it does not work with cookies.

IMPORTANT: Be very careful in using this item and think about what seeds you are planting and harvesting! Once used, it cannot be undone or refunded.

ONE MORE THING: It is best to plant crops one by one, so if you are using 'condensed view' in your Farm, you can go back to 'full' view under Farm Settings.
